data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Looking to move into a NEWER home NOW?  Amazing opportunity to own this beautiful house with a lot of upgrades ! This home has been well -maintained and looks practically new. It features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with a two car garage. This Kitchen area is perfect for entertaining guests and/or Family and friends. The Master Bedroom features a Master Bathroom containing a private toilet area, walk-in Closet and a linen closet. It features an extended driveway for all of your visitors.  There are NO CDD's and LOW HOA'S! Come check out this jewel before it's gone! No repairs AS IS.  The house has Solar panels included in the price.
